msgid "Determined to see for yourself, you made the journey west of Arkham to the blasted heath.  Over forty years later and the land is still blanched and forsaken.  As you walked the grounds, a luminous glow from the remains of the well drew your attention.  Splotches of colour began to seep up through the dead land, and before you could even reach the edge of the well, the glow flared with horrid brightness.  You fled at once, and only once you had run clear of the blighted land did the light die down and recede into the gray soil.  You escaped with your life and some knowledge of the dormant colour's spread throughout the affected land."
